comments: Dosunmu (CHI) makes contact to Dort's (OKC) arm that affects his SQBR.
Dort (OKC) makes marginal contact with DeRozan (CHI) during the drive that does not affect his SQBR.
DeRozan (CHI) makes marginal contact with Dort (OKC) as he disengages.
Dosunmu (CHI) makes marginal contact with Dort (OKC) that does not affect his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Williams (OKC) briefly engages with White (CHI) during the throw-in but does not affect his FOM.  Williams then loses his balance on his own.
Mann (OKC) reaches in and makes marginal contact to White's (CHI) body that does not affect his SQBR.
DeRozan (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Bazley (OKC) and the contact is incidental.
Vucevic (CHI) extends his off-arm and briefly places his hand on Dort's (OKC) shoulder.  The contact is marginal.
Jones Jr. (CHI) initiates contact to Dort's (OKC) body that affects his SQBR during the drive to the basket.
Vucevic (CHI) and Williams (OKC) make incidental contact with each other as Vucevic tips the loose ball away.
Wiggins (OKC) commits a take foul on DeRozan (CHI).

Brown Jr. (CHI) maintains a legal guarding position during Dort's (OKC) drive to the basket and shot attempt and the contact is incidental.
